classTweaker v1 official

# Better Hanging Signs cleanup reads the held item off a hanging ItemDisplay
# (BetterHangingSignsRemover#handleRoot). Display$ItemDisplay#getItemStack() is
# private in vanilla; widen it so the loader-agnostic common code can call it.
# Fabric: copied through as an accessWidener; NeoForge/Forge: translated to an
# accesstransformer.cfg entry by Allay.
accessible method net/minecraft/world/entity/Display$ItemDisplay getItemStack ()Lnet/minecraft/world/item/ItemStack;
